
# Change Log
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
 
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](http://keepachangelog.com/)
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org/).

## [0.3.0] - 2023-11-06

Implementing logging
Elasticsearch x OpenTelemetry - https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/apm/guide/current/open-telemetry.html

### Added
- logger.js - centralized module to obtain and configure logging

### Changed
- Downgraded exporter-logs-otlp-http to 0.43 as 0.44 is not functional

## [0.2.1] - 2023-10-30

All chages are made following: https://opentelemetry.io/docs/instrumentation/js/manual/#acquiring-a-tracer
 
### Added

 - tracer.js - centralized module to obtain a tracer for outputing manual spans

### Changed

 - dice.js - Added a manual span

## [0.2.0] - 2023-10-30

All chages are made following: https://opentelemetry.io/docs/instrumentation/js/manual
 
### Added

 - Jaeger.sh - script to run jaeger container
 - Jaeger was added as tracing exporter for opentelemetry
 - env.sh - script to export all necessary environment variables

### Changed

App architecture was changed in regards of contexts of files
 
## [0.1.0] - 2023-10-30

All chages are made following: https://opentelemetry.io/docs/instrumentation/js/getting-started/nodejs/
 
### Added

 - app.js - App entrypoint
 - instrumentation.js - opentelemetry configuration
